      def transform_text(text):
          text=text.lower()
          text=nltk.word_tokenize(text)
      ​
          y=[]
          for i in text:
              if i.isalnum():
                  y.append(i)
                  
                  
          text=y[:]
          y.clear()
              
          for i in text:
              if i not in stopwords.words('english') and i not in string.punctuation:
                  y.append(i)
                          
                          
          text =y[:]
          y.clear()
              
          for i in text:
              y.append(ps.stem(i))   
          return" ".join(y)
